TITLE: Installing @turf/turf Package via npm
DESCRIPTION: This command installs the @turf/turf package individually using npm. It allows users to add the Turf.js library to their project for geospatial analysis.
SOURCE: https://github.com/turfjs/turf/blob/master/packages/turf/README.md#2025-04-21_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: sh
