TITLE: Using Along Function with Turf.js in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: Example demonstrating how to create a point at a specified distance along a line using the @turf/along function. The function takes a line, distance value, and options object with unit specification.
SOURCE: https://github.com/turfjs/turf/blob/master/packages/turf-along/README.md#2025-04-21_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
var line = turf.lineString([[-83, 30], [-84, 36], [-78, 41]]);
var options = {units: 'miles'};

var along = turf.along(line, 200, options);

//addToMap
var addToMap = [along, line]
```

