TITLE: Generating Random Polygons with TurfJS in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: This code demonstrates how to generate a collection of random polygons within a specified bounding box using turf.randomPolygon(). The function returns a GeoJSON FeatureCollection of polygons.
SOURCE: https://github.com/turfjs/turf/blob/master/packages/turf-random/README.md#2025-04-21_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
var polygons = turf.randomPolygon(25, {bbox: [-180, -90, 180, 90]})
// => polygons
```

