SOURCE: https://github.com/turfjs/turf/blob/master/packages/turf-polygon-tangents/README.md#2025-04-21_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: sh
CODE:
```
$ npm install @turf/turf
```

----------------------------------------

TITLE: Installing @turf/polygonize module via npm
DESCRIPTION: Command to install the individual @turf/polygonize module using npm package manager.
SOURCE: https://github.com/turfjs/turf/blob/master/packages/turf-polygonize/README.md#2025-04-21_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: Shell
CODE:
```
$ npm install @turf/polygonize
```

----------------------------------------

TITLE: Installing the Triangle Grid Module Individually
DESCRIPTION: Command to install only the @turf/triangle-grid module as a standalone dependency via npm.
SOURCE: https://github.com/turfjs/turf/blob/master/packages/turf-triangle-grid/README.md#2025-04-21_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: sh
CODE:
```
$ npm install @turf/triangle-grid
```
